My first few moves were from the game database, because I knew if I wanted to beat someone rated much higher than me, I needed as many resources as I could possibly get.  I typically start my moves when I'm white with my pawn moving up two spaces.
Instead of my typical defense of the pawns, I decided to start out aggressive.
